Intro to Entre Movie Project

Show the data frame

library(jsonlite)
# load the json to a dataframe
dt <- read_json("/Users/jeffchiang/Git/IMDB-Crawler/IMDB/imdb_raw.json", simplifyVector = TRUE)
# clean the data
dt$index <- unlist(dt$index)
dt$year <- unlist(dt$year)
dt$url <- unlist(dt$url)
dt$title <- unlist(dt$title)
dt$certificate <- unlist(dt$certificate)
dt$runtime <- unlist(dt$runtime)
dt$rating <- unlist(dt$rating)
dt$votes <- unlist(dt$votes)
dt$gross <- unlist(dt$gross)
library('DT')
datatable(dt) # use dt package to visualize
It seems your data is too big for client-side DataTables. You may consider server-side processing: http://rstudio.github.io/DT/server.htmlIt seems your data is too big for client-side DataTables. You may consider server-side processing: http://rstudio.github.io/DT/server.html
